---
title: Asian Beef Rump & Radish Tacos with Creamy Slaw
description: Tacos with inspired by Asian cooking are coming together to make an unbeatable fusion of flavours. We've packed tortillas with
oyster sauce-glazed beef strips and added a colourful slaw with radish for a bit of peppery crunch. It’s the ultimate combination!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/663d566092f430b61ffd655d-812a7a62.jpeg
